File: GoogleÂ has been hit with big fines in the European Union for unfair competition, and has challenged those cases. (AFP) JOHANNESBURG - Google services are down across the globe. Users are experiencing issues with the Google system including YouTube, Gmail, Google Sheets and other core Google programmes.
Reports of issues began to surface this afternoon with hundreds of users taking to Twitter to vent. It's not yet clear what the source of the problem is and Google has not yet explained the reasons for the outage.